### Component 1: Core Pipeline Engine

#### [NEW] [auto_pipeline.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/auto_pipeline.py)

Backend orchestrator — không chứa UI code. Lấy lại logic từ các module có sẵn:

```python
class AutoPipeline:
    """Orchestrates: YouTube download → Chapter split → Style Rewrite."""
    
    def run_single(self, url, config, callbacks) -> dict:
        """Process 1 YouTube URL end-to-end."""
        # Step 1: Download transcript (reuse yt_downloader functions)
        # Step 2: Split chapters (reuse chapter_splitter functions)  
        # Step 3: Rewrite chapters (reuse rewriter functions)
    
    def run_batch_independent(self, urls, config, callbacks) -> list:
        """Process multiple URLs independently (1 script per URL)."""
    
    def run_batch_merged(self, urls, config, callbacks) -> dict:
        """Merge multiple transcripts → 1 combined script."""
```

**Tái sử dụng functions từ modules hiện có — KHÔNG duplicate code:**

| Step | Reuse From | Functions |
|------|-----------|-----------|
