**UI Features:**
- `QPlainTextEdit` cho paste nhiều URLs (1 per line)
- Auto-detect single vs multiple links
- Khi >1 link: popup hỏi "Independent scripts" hoặc "Merge into one"
- Visual pipeline stepper (3-step progress bar)
- `LogSection` (reuse existing widget)
- Config lưu/load qua `config_manager`

