## Pipeline Flow Detail

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start["User pastes URLs + clicks Run"] --> Count{"How many URLs?"}
    Count -->|1| Single["Single mode"]
    Count -->|>1| Ask{"Popup: Independent or Merge?"}
    Ask -->|Independent| Batch["Process each URL independently"]
    Ask -->|Merge| Merge["Merge mode"]
    
    Single --> DL1["Step 1: Download"]
    DL1 --> DL1a["get_video_info()"]
    DL1a --> DL1b["get_transcript_ytdlp() / fallback"]
    DL1b --> DL1c["extract_timestamps()"]
    DL1c --> DL1d["build_transcript_file()"]
    DL1d --> DL1e["(optional) download_video + thumb"]
    DL1e --> Split["Step 2: Split Chapters"]
    
    Split --> S1["classify_script_type()"]
    S1 --> S2["split_chapters()"]
    S2 --> S3["verify_chapters()"]
    S3 --> S4["punctuate_chapters() (if SRT)"]
    S4 --> S5["save_chapters() + merge_chapters()"]
    S5 --> Rewrite["Step 3: Rewrite"]
    
    Rewrite --> R1["Load chapters from 02_chapters/"]
    R1 --> R2{"script_type?"}
    R2 -->|top_list| R3["Top/List Review pipeline (12 steps)"]
    R2 -->|narrative| R4["Narrative pipeline (8 steps)"]
    R3 --> Done["✅ Complete"]
    R4 --> Done
    
    Batch --> DL1
    
    Merge --> MDL["Download all transcripts"]
    MDL --> MCombine["Concatenate transcript texts"]
    MCombine --> Split
```

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification (User Testing)

> [!NOTE]
> Project không có test suite. Verification sẽ bằng manual testing trên UI.

1. **Single URL test**: Paste 1 YouTube URL → Run → Verify:
   - Transcript downloaded to `01_download/`
   - Chapters split correctly in `02_chapters/`
   - Rewritten chapters in `03_rewrite/`
   - Folder structure đúng format

2. **Multiple URL - Independent test**: Paste 3 URLs → Choose "Independent" → Verify:
   - 3 separate project folders created
   - Each runs the full pipeline independently

3. **Multiple URL - Merge test**: Paste 2 URLs → Choose "Merge" → Verify:
   - Transcripts merged thành 1 file
   - Chapters split từ merged text
   - Rewrite chạy trên merged chapters

4. **Stop/Pause test**: Start pipeline → Pause midway → Resume → Verify nó tiếp tục đúng step

5. **Error handling test**: Paste invalid URL → Verify error logged, không crash app
